| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5996 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2225bee8-a4a7-5e23-99a3-a14e3955f998"
